 \lim_{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{2^n (n!)^2}{(2n+1)!} = 0, 
a_n = \dfrac{2^n(n!)^2}{(2n+1)!}
\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n} = \frac{2^{n+1}\bigl((n+1)!\bigr)^2(2n+1)!}{2^n(n!)^2(2n+3)!} = \frac{2(n+1)^2}{(2n+2)(2n+3)} = \frac{n+1}{2n+3} < \frac12.
