 \lim_{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{2^n (n!)^2}{(2n+1)!}= \lim_{n \rightarrow \infty}  \frac{C2^n (n^{n+\frac 12} e^{-n})^2}{(2n+1)^{2n+1+\frac 12} e^{-2n-1}}\\ =\lim_{n \rightarrow \infty}  C2^ne \frac{1}{(2n+1)^{\frac 12}} (\frac{n}{2n+1})^{2n+1}\\ =\lim_{n \rightarrow \infty}  C2^ne \frac{1}{(2n+1)^{\frac 12}}(\frac{1}{2})^{2n+1} (\frac{n}{n+\frac 12})^{2n+1}\\ =\lim_{n \rightarrow \infty}  Ce \frac{1}{(2n+1)^{\frac 12}}(\frac{1}{2})^{n+1} (\frac{1}{e})\\ =\lim_{n \rightarrow \infty}  \frac{C}{2^{n+1}(2n+1)^{\frac 12}} 
